---
import Icon from '@components/Icon.astro';
import { waLink } from '@/consts';
---

<section
	id='inicio'
	class='px-6 pt-12'
>
	<div class='mx-auto max-w-[860px] text-center'>
		<div
			class='mb-[26px] inline-flex items-center gap-[9px] rounded-full border border-[#ece2d2] bg-white px-4 py-2 text-[12.5px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[1.2px] text-copper-dark shadow-[0_8px_20px_-14px_rgba(74,79,84,0.4)] max-[530px]:justify-center max-[530px]:px-10 max-[530px]:text-center'
		>
			<span
				class='size-2 rounded-full bg-copper max-[530px]:hidden'
				aria-hidden='true'></span>
			Asesoría inmobiliaria<span class='max-[530px]:hidden'>&nbsp;·&nbsp;República Dominicana</span>
		</div>

		<h1
			class='mb-[22px] font-heading text-[clamp(36px,5.4vw,66px)] font-semibold leading-[1.05] tracking-[-1px] text-ink'
		>
			Tu próximo hogar, con un trato <span class='text-copper'>cercano y honesto.</span>
		</h1>

		<p class='mx-auto mb-[34px] max-w-[620px] text-[clamp(17px,1.5vw,20px)] font-light leading-[1.7] text-slate-soft'>
			Casas, apartamentos, solares y proyectos en planos en toda República Dominicana. Como el inventario cambia cada
			semana, <strong class='font-bold text-slate'
				>escríbenos por WhatsApp y te decimos qué tenemos disponible hoy.</strong
			>
		</p>

		<div class='flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-[14px]'>
			<a
				href={waLink()}
				target='_blank'
				rel='noopener'
				class='inline-flex items-center gap-[10px] rounded-full bg-copper px-[30px] py-4 text-base font-bold text-white shadow-[0_14px_30px_-12px_rgba(205,161,118,0.85)] transition-colors hover:bg-copper-dark'
			>
				<Icon
					name='whatsapp'
					size={25}
				/>
				Consultar disponibilidad
			</a>
			<a
				href='#que-trabajamos'
				class='inline-flex items-center rounded-full border-[1.5px] border-[#e2d8c8] bg-white px-7 py-[15px] text-base font-bold text-slate transition-colors hover:border-copper hover:text-copper-dark'
			>
				Conócenos
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>

	<!-- Hero image card -->
	<div class='relative mx-auto mt-[54px] max-w-[1180px]'>
		<div
			class='relative aspect-[3/2] overflow-hidden rounded-[28px] shadow-[0_50px_90px_-40px_rgba(74,79,84,0.55)] sm:aspect-[21/9]'
		>
			<img
				src='/img/hero.webp'
				alt='Interior cálido y luminoso de un hogar moderno con sala, comedor y cocina abiertos.'
				class='size-full object-cover'
				width='1600'
				height='686'
				fetchpriority='high'
			/>
		</div>
		<div
			class='mt-4 rounded-[18px] bg-[#fbf8f3]/95 px-[22px] py-4 text-left shadow-[0_24px_50px_-24px_rgba(74,79,84,0.5)] backdrop-blur-sm max-md:text-center md:absolute md:bottom-6 md:left-6 md:mt-0'
		>
			<p class='font-heading text-[19px] font-semibold text-ink'>Casas · Apartamentos · Solares · Planos</p>
			<p class='mt-0.5 text-[13.5px] text-gray-soft'>acompañamiento total, ya sea para vivir o invertir</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
